<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.6">
<l>arakkiya rākam pulleṉa villā laṇimati ḷilaṅkaiyar kōṉai</l>
<l>cerukkaḻit tamarar paṇiyamuṉ ṉiṉṟa cēvaka mōceyta tiṉṟu</l>
<l>murukkitaḻ vāycci muṉkaiveṇ caṅkam koṇṭumuṉ ṉēniṉṟu pōkāy</l>
<l>erukkilaik kāka veṟimaḻu vōcca leṉceyva tentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Why now the heroics that [you] did for which the gods stood before [you]</l>
<l rend="indent">as they bowed, [you] having destroyed in battle with a bow</l>
<l>The king of those of ornate-walled Laṅkā,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the breasts of the demon ladies paled?</l>
<l>Having taken the white [conch] bangles from the forearm of the girl</l>
<l rend="indent">with lips [like] a coral tree petal,</l>
<l>Remaining before [her eyes], you do not leave [her thoughts].</l>
<l rend="indent">My lord, my father, why this performance</l>
<l rend="indent">of casting a hurling axe for a milkweed leaf?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
